text:
The BEST and most AUTHENTIC old school biscuits of all times!
Strongly recommended.
If you are a 90s kid you would definitely have to come down to this shop and but the biscuits!
Brought me down memory lane...
I came finding for this shop after eating their cashew biscuit at SpaJelita.
500g $5.50 very affordable and fresh.
Many different household products and owners are friendly
